title: Valar Rereadis: A Storm of Swords Review
description:
A review of the characters arcs and themes in book 3. Featuring guests Lady Gwyn, Ser Buckley and Nina Friel. We discuss our favorite chapters, the 5 year gap, why this is the most popular book of the series, and quite a lot more!
